# Delete Session Modals

This section contains modals for the Delete Session workflow in the Pre-Session toolkit.

## Modal Structure

Each modal follows the established pattern:
- Single Storybook story file per modal
- Uses design system components (Modal, Button, Radio, etc.)
- Semantic spacing, color, and typography tokens
- No hardcoded values

## Components Used

- **Modal**: Main modal container from design system
- **Button**: Primary, outline, and danger variants
- **Radio**: Form radio buttons for selection
- **DatePicker**: Date range selection
- **Badge**: Status indicators
- **SupervisorManagementButtons**: Cancel/Confirm actions

## Tokens

- **Modal**: `--size-modal-pad-*`, `--size-modal-gap-*`, `--size-modal-radius-*`
- **Element**: `--size-element-gap-*`, `--size-element-pad-*`, `--size-element-radius-*`
- **Color**: `--color-surface-container-*`, `--color-primary`, `--color-danger`
- **Typography**: `h4`, `body2-txt`, etc.
